<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Job Club Privacy Notice</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
  </head>
  <body>
    <main class="privacy-page">
      <section class="panel">
        <div class="brand">
          <span class="mark">JC</span>
          <div>
            <h1>Privacy Notice</h1>
            <p>Job Club client portal</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="privacy-copy">
          <h2>What we collect</h2>
          <p>We collect the details you provide when joining Job Club, including your name, contact details, course notes, goal scores, messages, and any CV files you upload.</p>

          <h2>Why we collect it</h2>
          <p>We use this information to support you through the Job Club course, track your progress, communicate with you, and help with CVs, applications, interviews, and employment goals.</p>

          <h2>Who can see it</h2>
          <p>Your Job Club leader or authorised team members can see your information. You can log in to view and update your own record.</p>

          <h2>How long we keep it</h2>
          <p>We only keep your information for as long as it is needed to support you and run the Job Club safely. You can ask the Job Club leader about deleting your record.</p>

          <h2>CV uploads</h2>
          <p>CVs may contain personal information. Upload only files you are happy for your Job Club leader to view for the purpose of supporting your job search.</p>

          <h2>Your choice</h2>
          <p>If you do not want your information stored in this portal, speak to your Job Club leader about another way to take part.</p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
